# 파생변수 만들기
# 3 sigma 범위 내에 있는 값을 정상( = 0 ) / 범위 밖에 있는 값을 이상( = 1 )으로 분류하는 파생변수 생성
df['y_1'] = ((df['Z1_Temp'] > (np.mean(df['Z1_Temp']) + 3 * np.std(df['Z1_Temp']))) 
             | (df['Z1_Temp'] < (np.mean(df['Z1_Temp']) - 3 * np.std(df['Z1_Temp'])))).astype(int)
df['y_2'] = ((df['Z1_OP1'] > (np.mean(df['Z1_OP1']) + 3 * np.std(df['Z1_OP1']))) 
             | (df['Z1_OP1'] < (np.mean(df['Z1_OP1']) - 3 * np.std(df['Z1_OP1'])))).astype(int)
df['y_3'] = ((df['ST'] > (np.mean(df['ST']) + 3 * np.std(df['ST']))) 
             | (df['ST'] < (np.mean(df['ST']) - 3 * np.std(df['ST'])))).astype(int)
df['y_4'] = ((df['Tube_Furnace1_OP'] > (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace1_OP']) + 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace1_OP']))) 
             | (df['Tube_Furnace1_OP'] < (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace1_OP']) - 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace1_OP'])))).astype(int)

df['y_5'] = ((df['Tube_Furnace2_OP'] > (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace2_OP']) + 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace2_OP']))) 
             | (df['Tube_Furnace2_OP'] < (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace2_OP']) - 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace2_OP'])))).astype(int)
df['y_6'] = ((df['Tube_Furnace3_OP'] > (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace3_OP']) + 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace3_OP']))) 
             | (df['Tube_Furnace3_OP'] < (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace3_OP']) - 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace3_OP'])))).astype(int)
df['y_7'] = ((df['Tube_Furnace4_OP'] > (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace4_OP']) + 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace4_OP']))) 
             | (df['Tube_Furnace4_OP'] < (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace4_OP']) - 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace4_OP'])))).astype(int)
df['y_8'] = ((df['Tube_Furnace_CP'] > (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace_CP']) + 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace_CP']))) 
             | (df['Tube_Furnace_CP'] < (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace_CP']) - 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace_CP'])))).astype(int)

df['y_9'] = ((df['Tube_Furnace1_Temp'] > (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace1_Temp']) + 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace1_Temp']))) 
             | (df['Tube_Furnace1_Temp'] < (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace1_Temp']) - 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace1_Temp'])))).astype(int)
df['y_10'] = ((df['Tube_Furnace2_Temp'] > (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace2_Temp']) + 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace2_Temp']))) 
             | (df['Tube_Furnace2_Temp'] < (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace2_Temp']) - 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace2_Temp'])))).astype(int)
df['y_11'] = ((df['Tube_Furnace3_Temp'] > (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace3_Temp']) + 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace3_Temp']))) 
             | (df['Tube_Furnace3_Temp'] < (np.mean(df['Tube_Furnace3_Temp']) - 3 * np.std(df['Tube_Furnace3_Temp'])))).astype(int)

chi, pval, dof, expected = stats.chi2_contingency(chi_table)

print('p:{0:0}'.format(pval))
print('degree pf freedom:{}'.format(dof))
print('expected value:\n{}'.format(expected.round(1)))

df_Y_1 = df[df['Y'] == 1]['Z1_Temp']
In [87]:
# 등분산성
stats.bartlett(df_Y_0, df_Y_1)
Out[87]:
BartlettResult(statistic=35954.86904125169, pvalue=0.0)
In [88]:
# 등분산이 아님을 확인
In [90]:
t_result = stats.ttest_ind(df_Y_0, df_Y_1, equal_var=False)
t, p = t_result.statistic.round(3), t_result.pvalue.round(3)

print('2-sample-t-test')
print('t 통계량 : {}'.format(t))
print('p-value : {}'.format(p))

# 등분산성
print(stats.bartlett(df_Y_0, df_Y_1))

t_result = stats.ttest_ind(df_Y_0, df_Y_1, equal_var=False)
t, p = t_result.statistic.round(3), t_result.pvalue

print('2-sample-t-test')

print('p-value : {}'.format(p))
